  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3658598">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3658598/" class="title-link">让心灵快速吃饱的方便面</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3658598"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/41416923/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u41416923-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/41416923/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">慢运动</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-08"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-08 21:42:29</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3658598_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  是于丹把从不看国学书的我吸引到关注国学书籍之上。不过，于丹的书、讲座，只是一碗鸡汤，喝着香，但过了就忘了。而傅老师的书，用最短的时间让我迈入国学之门，为博大精深的中国古代哲学思想所折服。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">2有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
