  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2135242">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2135242/" class="title-link">一本容易看懂的书</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2135242"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2640875/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2640875-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2640875/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Summer</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-07-13"
      class="main-meta">2009-07-13 09:17:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2135242_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                      以前看了一些关于国学的书，都讲得太空、深，看起来不是很明白。傅佩荣老师的这本书相对来说是一本比较简单的书，书中的内容很清晰，易读、易懂。     从孔孟老庄几个方面向我们介绍了国学。让我们学会真诚，增加智慧。 

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2135242/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2135242_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2135242_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



