              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/33218786/" class="">孔子的真诚</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/98208747/" class=" " title="趴在云上看海">趴在云上看海</a>
              
